You can simply ask Alexa to control your Aquário Haus products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our Aquário Haus app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in Aquário Haus app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable Aquário Haus skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell to Echo " Alexa discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on the bedroom light"
"Alexa, turn off the bedroom light"
